    "body" : "<p>It's actually rather easy. Just do this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>BigDecimal test = new BigDecimal(0);\nSystem.out.println(test);\ntest = test.add(new BigDecimal(30));\nSystem.out.println(test);\ntest = test.add(new BigDecimal(45));\nSystem.out.println(test);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>See also: <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/math/BigDecimal.html#add%28java.math.BigDecimal%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>BigDecimal#add(java.math.BigDecimal)</code></a></p>\n"
