    "body" : "<pre><code>BigDecimal demo = new BigDecimal(15);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It is immutable beacuse it internally store you input i.e (15) as  <code>final private final BigInteger intVal;</code>\nand same concept use at the time of string creation every input finally store in \n<code>private final char value[];</code>.So there is no implmented bug.</p>\n"
