    "body" : "<p>Using Java8 lambdas </p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;BigDecimal&gt; items = Arrays.asList(a, b, c, .....);\n\nitems.stream().filter(Objects::nonNull).reduce(BigDecimal.ZERO, BigDecimal::add);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This covers cases where the some or all of the objects in the list is null.</p>\n"
