  "title" : "Addition for BigDecimal",
  "body" : "<p>I want to do some simple sums with some currency values expressed in <code>BigDecimal</code> type. </p>\n\n<pre><code>BigDecimal test = new BigDecimal(0);\nSystem.out.println(test);\ntest.add(new BigDecimal(30));\nSystem.out.println(test);\ntest.add(new BigDecimal(45));\nSystem.out.println(test);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Obviously I do not understand well the <code>BigDecimal</code> arithmetics, see output behind.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Test\n0\n0\n0\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Can anyone help me out?</p>\n"
